<br>
Necklace - reduces component usage<br>
Mantle - increases the duration of buff spells<br>
Earring - either reduces aggro generated by spells (the official explanation) or reduces mana usage (the results that are showing up in player tests).<br>
Ring - decreases casting time<br>
Bracelet - increases spell damage<br>
<br>
There are also some very nice new summons such as the Elemental Defender (10 AC, fire and cold resistances, shield or back slot - all non-caster classes) and complete sets of summoned armor. They are especially nifty for equipping your pets, as well as making you loved by other characters. They are available at the mage guild in Shadow Haven.<br>
<br>
If you don't have the Luclin expansion, there are those of us who are willing to drop by and grab the spells for our colleagues.<br>
